				<div class="clear"></div>
				<div class="body">
					<p>Great post - I've been interested in checking out jQuery for a while now but my JavaScript skills aren't the best. I am wondering what modifications would need to be made with your code to get it to work with a structure like this:</p>
<p>    Task<br />
    Time</br></p>
<p>      Project<br />
